     <!-- &lt;div style="width: 100%; height: 93%; clear:both;"&gt; -->
     <div id="map-canvas" style=" width:100%;">

     <!-- &lt;/div&gt; -->
     <script>
      var swindow_height = parseInt($( window ).height()) - 95;
$("#mainMapDev").css("height",swindow_height+'px');
$("#map-canvas").css("height",swindow_height+'px');


var markerClusterer;
var map;
var currentLat;
var currentLong;
var currentMarker;
var geocoder;
var video_data = [];
var videoDataArray = [];
var video_id = "3299";
var pilot = "";
var current_user_lat = "";
var current_user_long = "";

var markers_r = [];
var markers_y = [];
var markers_p = [];
var markers_o = [];
var markers_g = [];

var markerCluster_r;
var markerCluster_y;
var markerCluster_p;
var markerCluster_o;
var markerCluster_g;
var switchMarkerCount=1;
/*
 * Function to initialze google Map with clusters .
 */

var bounds;
function initialize(video_data) {
	var minZoomLevel = 3;
    window.map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("map-canvas"), {
        mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP
    });

    bounds = new google.maps.LatLngBounds();
	createMarker(video_data)
    //map.fitBounds(bounds);
    var listener = google.maps.event.addListener(map, "idle", function () {

    	map.setCenter(new google.maps.LatLng("32.7833333","-96.7970"));
        map.setZoom(8);
        google.maps.event.removeListener(listener);
    });
    google.maps.event.addListener(map, 'zoom_changed', function() {
        if (map.getZoom() &lt; minZoomLevel) map.setZoom(minZoomLevel);
      });
  
       
}

function createMarker(video_data)
{
			//for (var i = 0; i &lt; video_data.length; i++)
			for(var i in video_data)
			{
				//var infowindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow();
				var marker = new google.maps.Marker({
				position: new google.maps.LatLng(video_data[i].lat,video_data[i].long),
				map: map,
				video_id: video_data[i].rowId,
				icon: 'http://travelbydrone.com/assets/images/cluster_images/' + video_data[i].image,
				lat: video_data[i].lat,
				long: video_data[i].long,
				type: video_data[i].type,
				url : video_data[i].url,
			});
			
			bounds.extend(marker.position);
			
			//set current marker for direct vidoe
			if(video_id == video_data[i].rowId)
			{
				currentMarker = marker;
			}
			
			if(video_data[i].type=='DEF')
			{
				markers_r.push(marker);
			}
			else if(video_data[i].type=='LAT' || video_data[i].type=='P')
			{
				markers_y.push(marker);
			}
			else if(video_data[i].type=='POP')
			{
				markers_p.push(marker);
			}
			else if(video_data[i].type=='BST')
			{
				markers_o.push(marker);
			}
			else if(video_data[i].type=='FEV')
			{
				markers_g.push(marker);
			}
			
			google.maps.event.addListener(marker, 'click', function() {
				var video_third_party_url = this.url;
				currentLat = this.lat;
				currentLong = this.long;
				currentMarker = this;
				
				var video_url = 'http://travelbydrone.com/play/'+this.video_id;
				if(video_url!=window.location &amp;&amp; this.type!='P')
				{
					window.history.pushState({path:video_url},'',video_url);	
				}
	
				var detailUrl = this.url;
				if(this.type!='P')
				{
					detailUrl = "http://travelbydrone.com/drone/viewVideo/"+this.video_id;
				}
				
				$.magnificPopup.open({
						items: {
							type: 'ajax',
							modal:false,
							src: detailUrl,
							closeOnContentClick: false,
						},
					});
			});
		}
		
		createCluster('v');
}

function createCluster(clusterType)
{
		if(clusterType=='v')
		{
			markerCluster_r = new MarkerClusterer(map, markers_r, {
				styles:[
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster1.png',
					height: 50,
					width: 50,
				    opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster2.png',
					height: 60,
					width: 60,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster3.png',
					height: 80,
					width: 80,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0]
				}
			]
		});
		
			markerCluster_p = new MarkerClusterer(map, markers_p, {
				styles:[
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster1featured.png',
					height: 50,
					width: 50,
				    opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster2featured.png',
					height: 60,
					width: 60,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster3featured.png',
					height: 80,
					width: 80,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0]
				}
			]
		});
	
			markerCluster_o = new MarkerClusterer(map, markers_o, {
				styles:[
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster1editors.png',
					height: 50,
					width: 50,
				    opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster2editors.png',
					height: 60,
					width: 60,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster3editors.png',
					height: 80,
					width: 80,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0]
				}
			]
		});

			markerCluster_g = new MarkerClusterer(map, markers_g, {
				styles:[
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster1favourite.png',
					height: 50,
					width: 50,
				    opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster2favourite.png',
					height: 60,
					width: 60,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster3favourite.png',
					height: 80,
					width: 80,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0]
				}
			]
		});

			if(switchMarkerCount==1)
			{
				markerCluster_y = new MarkerClusterer(map, markers_y, {
				styles:[
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster1latest.png',
					height: 50,
					width: 50,
				    opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster2latest.png',
					height: 60,
					width: 60,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster3latest.png',
					height: 80,
					width: 80,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0]
				}
			]
		});
				switchMarkerCount=2;
			}
			markerCluster_y.clearMarkers();
		}
		else
		{
			markerCluster_y = new MarkerClusterer(map, markers_y, {
				styles:[
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster1latest.png',
					height: 50,
					width: 50,
				    opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster2latest.png',
					height: 60,
					width: 60,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0],
					textColor: '#fff'
				},
				{
					url: base_url+'assets/images/cluster_images/cluster3latest.png',
					height: 80,
					width: 80,
					opt_anchor: [0, 0]
				}
			]
		});
		
			markerCluster_r.clearMarkers();
			markerCluster_p.clearMarkers();
			markerCluster_o.clearMarkers();
			markerCluster_g.clearMarkers();
		}
		setTimeout('$("#progress_div").hide()',1000);
}
